<!-- ============================================================
     FILE 6: TOOL DEFINITIONS

     Tool definitions for the Hermes function calling system.
     These go inside <tools></tools> XML tags in the system prompt.

     Hermes uses OpenAI-compatible JSON schema format.
     The runtime auto-registers tools from its tool registry,
     but custom tools can be defined here for reference or
     for direct system prompt injection.

     Format reference:
       <tools>[...tool definitions...]</tools>

     Each tool call by the model:
       <tool_call>
       {"name": "tool_name", "arguments": {"key": "value"}}
       </tool_call>

     Each tool response:
       <tool_response>
       {"name": "tool_name", "content": {...}}
       </tool_response>
     ============================================================ -->
